Heat grill and grill basket. Toss shrimp and peppers with 1/4 cup of the sauce. Pour into grill basket. Cover and cook over medium-high heat for 5 to 6 minutes, stirring occasionally, until shrimp are just bright pink and peppers are crisp tender. Meanwhile, heat rice as directed on package. Toss shrimp with remaining 1/4 cup sauce. Serve over hot cooked rice.